### Teste do fluxo de pagamento fake

### 1. Primeiro, criar um cliente
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Cliente Teste",
  "email": "teste@email.com",
  "cpf": "11144477735"
}

### 2. Criar um produto
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Hambúrguer Teste",
  "description": "Hambúrguer para teste de pagamento",
  "category": "Lanche",
  "price": 25.50
}

### 3. Criar um pedido
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "{{CUSTOMER_ID}}",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "{{PRODUCT_ID}}",
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ]
}

### 4. Fazer checkout (gerar QR Code)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/orders/{{ORDER_ID}}/checkout

### 5. Confirmar pagamento (usar o QR Code retornado no passo 4)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/orders/{{ORDER_ID}}/confirm-payment
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "qrCode": "{{QR_CODE_FROM_CHECKOUT}}"
}
